title: Ep. #20 | Catching Up: Jae of Day6
description:
We are back with another edition of “Catching Up”, this time featuring the KING OF TWITTER himself, Jae of DAY6! Jae and Eric discuss just about everything, including correcting errors in Jae’s biography, transitioning to Korea, perks of being in a group, answering your questions, and so much more. Make sure to follow us on all our socials @daebakshow and watch video highlights of each episode on Youtube at www.youtube.com/divestudios We hope you enjoy! #jae #day6 #jaeofday6 #daebakshow #ericnam
